casebody.data:
In re Moones MELLOULI; Moones Mellouli,
v.
Loretta E. Lynch, Attorney General. No. 15-436, 15-437 (R46-011). Supreme Court of the United States Dec. 4, 2015.

The petition for writ of mandamus and/or prohibition and the petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit were dismissed today pursuant to Rule 46.1 of the Rules of this Court.
